name: MSRI-QUADRO-GIFRainbow-IWh-01
description: v4w.enko - "MSRI-QUADRO-GIFRainbow-IWh-01" is a gif animation of  3d Object, generated with custom definition. 1 loft is animated in 1 layer in Rainbow colors. The cells of the Indigo  "3d voronoi" cube are linked to the attractor`s points of the loft. Another one group of cells linked to the same attractor`s points  and are rotating as the white cube. The parallel projections are showing the different viewpoints of the same form. Top, Back, Front, Bottom. Total 128 frames, 1024*1024px canvas.
